contentrichtext.text: [[Image:Posen kr Schubin.jpg|thumb|right]] '''Kreis Schubin''' was a [[Kreis in Prussia]] (county) in the northern administrative [[Bromberg district|district of Bromberg]], in the [[province of Posen]]. ==History== {{Empty section|date=July 2010}} ==Geographical features== {{Empty section|date=July 2010}} == Table of Standesämter == "Standesamt" is the German name of the local civil registration offices which were established in October 1874 soon after the German Empire was formed. Births, marriages and deaths were recorded.
